#

Arugula and Goat Cheese Salad

10 min
$8
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Starter

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthy

Description

A fresh and vibrant salad combining peppery arugula, creamy goat cheese, and a tangy dressing.

Ingredients

  • arugula: 4 cups
  • goat cheese: 4 oz
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
